  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To prospectively monitor the survival rate of Ankylos® dental implants, comparing delayed
      versus immediate loading, using abutments with the SynCone® concept for implant-supported
      detachable dental prosthesis (ISDDP) in the edentulous upper jaw.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
